      <title>E.ON、Sabanci 聘请花旗银行和摩根大通负责电力生产商 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/e-on-sabanci-said-to-hire-citi-jpmorgan-for-power-producer-ipo</link>
